title: Spacious 1 Bedroom 1 Bath with Walk-In Closet and Balcony
posting_body: ['KNOLLWOOD TOWERS WEST', 'Welcome to Knollwood Towers West Apartments in Hopkins, Minnesota!', 'Knollwood Towers West offers studio, one bedroom or two bedroom units in this 7 story building.', 'Enjoy the new fitness center and underground parking.', 'Every apartment has a generously sized balcony with an east, west, north or south view.', 'Located off the main road and adjacent to Oakes Park with play structures for children, tennis courts and ball fields.', 'Call today to schedule your personal tour!', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Want more information on this unit?', 'See link (below):', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 620 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Patio/Balcony', '- Air Conditioner', '- Cable Ready', '- Dishwasher', '- Refrigerator', 'Community Amenities', '- Fitness Center', '- Laundry Facilities', '- Elevator', '- Community Room', '- Short Walk to Metro Transit Bus Line', '- Controlled Access/Gated', 'Pet Policy', 'NO PETS', 'Income Requirements:', '2.5 MONTHLY RENT', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Knollwood Towers West', '1010 Lake St. Ne, Hopkins, MN, 55343', 'yvEtGS4Lw']
